1.3 Формулы¶

:

:

, . :

$$ Recovery = \frac{C \times (F - T)}{F \times (C - T)} \times100\% $$

:

  • C /;
  • F / /;
  • T /.

. , .

:

sMAPE (. Symmetric Mean Absolute Percentage Error, ).
MAE, , . , .

sMAPE :

$$ sMAPE = \frac{1}{N} \sum\limits_{i=1}^N\frac{|y_i - y'_i|}{(|y_i| + |y'_i|) / 2} \times 100\% $$

.

sMAPE:

$$ overall\_sMAPE = 25\% \times sMAPE(rougher) + 75\% \times sMAPE(final) $$

def na_values(data):
    
    full_columns=[]
    na_columns=[]
    
    for column in data:
        if data[column].isna().sum()==0:
            full_columns.append(column)
        if data[column].isna().sum()!=0:
            na_columns.append(column)
    return(len(full_columns), len(na_columns), round(len(na_columns)/ len(data.columns)* 100))

4 Обучение моделей¶

4.1 Функция для вычисления итоговой sMAPE¶

(SMAPE sMAPE). .

In [31]:
#    SMAPE

def smape(target, predict):
    smape = (1/len(target))*np.sum((np.abs(target - predict))/( (np.abs(target)+np.abs(predict))/2))*100
    return smape
In [32]:
#  

smape_scorer = make_scorer(smape, greater_is_better = False)
In [33]:
#     SMAPE 

def overall_smape(rougher, final):
    overall = 0.25*rougher+0.75*final
    return overall
